MKL
-----------------------------------------------------
 * Download the latest Intel MKL
 * Run the install.sh script
 * Choose to do a 'custom' install
 * Set the installation path to <BOOTIMAGE>/src/mkl

ACML
-----------------------------------------------------
 * Download the latest ACML from AMD
 * Run the install script
 * Install to a writable location of your choice
 * Copy or symlink 'gfortran_mp' from install src to  <BOOTIMAGE>/src/gfortran_mp

